          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Community Energy Savings Program Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Energy to establish a grant program for states and Indian tribes to provide loans to consumers and communities that want to implement cost-effective energy efficiency measures.</p>]]>
